title: Dunford Discusses Middle East Challenges With Israeli Leaders (US Department of Defense)
text: ( Source : US Department of Defense ) JERUSALEM, October 18 , 2015 - The chairman of the Joint Chiefs of Staff discussed a full range of threats in the Middle East with Israeli Prime Minister Benjamin Netanyahu and other Israeli officials
